{"tid":2272139,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"襲警案作供士沙 被揭曾裁不可靠","createTime":"2020-11-05T02:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T02:08:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"32c8da6c41b620be7a545947bab9165cfc8fe394","tid":2272139,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:08:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/6PZJFWTKTJCORKSGQ5MMEGAACQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2F6PZJFWTKTJCORKSGQ5MMEGAACQ%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4NTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=1f34994b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2F6PZJFWTKTJCORKSGQ5MMEGAACQ%2F&h=2563fddc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/6PZJFWTKTJCORKSGQ5MMEGAACQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n襲警案作供士沙 被揭曾裁不可靠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J_XAKfQLRyPexx9s8Zgpkd8eTPw=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ADBAA4J4YBDODP6TYIFGAQZSGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ_XAKfQLRyPexx9s8Zgpkd8eTPw%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FADBAA4J4YBDODP6TYIFGAQZSGU.jpg&h=26e0aeab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警署警長林華平<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年9月網民發起「和你飛2.0」，。。。。。。。。。，警長對被翻舊賬顯得不忿，反駁稱辯方的提問亦與本案無關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不忿指與本案無關<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林華平供稱，目擊。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問林時引述黃大仙暴動案，指沈官裁定他為「不可靠證人」，更批評他未有如實向法庭道出真相。林僅稱只知當時表證成立，又稱所屬小隊在反送中運動期間拘捕上百人，他亦拘捕過「幾個人」。辯方指事隔一年多，林會否有可能將本案細節與其他案件混淆？林笑言「絕對有咁嘅可能」，後澄清不會混淆被告的衣着容貌。丁家豪則供稱當晚他欲扶起一名女子時，被告突衝出用雨傘兩度揮打，他被推倒地，被告逃走被林華平制服。辯方播片指追截路徑「九曲十三彎」，丁則堅稱被告一直在視線範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官徐綺薇裁定表面證供成立。被告不自辯，辯方今結案陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTS3006/20"}]}